_sText:
Map Name: Fy_HeLL
Version: 1.0

Description: Fy_HeLL is based on our most popular map which is played on our servers. Fy_HeLL is a re-make of that map, our version is
Guaranteed to be More Fun. More Challenging. Bigger Which cuts down on the Wrath of AWPs! 
And The Map has a "Red" Theme to go along with ]HeLL[ Clans background.
I can almost guarantee that this map will be great on 8 v 8 Servers!
There is a Buyzone in the middle, where you can buy the all important M3!!
Plenty of Nades on the side of the walls and Different guns which are placed on the floor. Given that they come already equiped with FULL Ammunation.
Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!
www.hellclan.co.uk
